Package com.lpvs.entity.dashboard

package com.lpvs.entity.dashboard
This package contains entity classes related to the dashboard functionality in the LPVS system. Entities in this package represent various elements and metrics used for visualizing system information. The LPVS system uses these entities to present aggregated data, statistics, and trends to users through dashboards.

These classes are designed to provide a comprehensive view of system activity, including license detections, issue counts, participant statistics, and repository metrics.

The dashboard functionality is crucial for users to monitor and analyze the status of the LPVS system over time.
